---
title: Smoky Campfire-Style Sausage with Homemade Baked Beans and Buttery Mash
description: Baked beans are one of our ultimate comfort foods from childhood, and we're upping the ante here by serving a tasty, smoky mixed bean medley with mash and delicious sausages. One taste and they'll be back on your all-time faves list!
